arStrings.szText: Aneta's already gone. You won't see her again.
Matter of factly. This is the way it had to be. Pronounciation: Ah-net-uh
But she left you a letter, there on the table.
In contrast with the previous line, you break your cold exterior and try to be a bit warm. The player wasn't able to say goodbye to your student but you know how important she was to them.
